"title": "6237: sexual sin, nature of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6237",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Any transgression of the limits that God has set for the enjoyment of sex. Such sins are often life-dominating, but may be broken through the power and grace of Jesus Christ.</p>\n<h2>The origin of sexual sin</h2>\n<h3>Fallen human nature</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:19\">GAL 5:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:12-Rom13:14\">ROM 13:12–13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:5-Col3:6\">COL 3:5–3:6</a></p>\n<h3>The heart</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:19\">MAT 15:19</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:21-Mark7:22\">MRK 7:21–7:22</a></p>\n<h2>The offensiveness of sexual sin</h2>\n<h3>It defiles the sinner</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:20\">MAT 15:20</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:23\">MRK 7:23</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:24\">ROM 1:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:18\">1CO 6:18</a></p>\n<h3>It defiles society</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev18:24-Lev18:25\">LEV 18:24–18:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:6\">1CO 5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:2\">REV 19:2</a></p>\n<h3>It offends other people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:7-2Pet2:8\">2PE 2:7–2:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:22-Gen9:25\">GEN 9:22–9:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen34:7\">GEN 34:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen38:24\">GEN 38:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:21-2Sam13:22\">2SA 13:21–13:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:21\">2CO 12:21</a></p>\n<h3>It offends God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam11:27\">2SA 11:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer13:26-Jer13:27\">JER 13:26–13:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:5\">MAL 3:5</a></p>\n<h2>Sexual sin under the old covenant</h2>\n<h3>Pre-marital sex</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:13-Deut22:21\">DEU 22:13–22:21</a></p>\n<h3>Adultery</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:14\">EXO 20:14</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:18\">DEU 5:18</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev18:20\">LEV 18:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:22-Deut22:24\">DEU 22:22–22:24</a></p>\n<h3>Prostitution</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:29\">LEV 19:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut23:17-Deut23:18\">DEU 23:17–23:18</a></p>\n<h3>Rape</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:25-Deut22:29\">DEU 22:25–22:29</a></p>\n<h3>Homosexual intercourse</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev18:22\">LEV 18:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:13\">LEV 20:13</a></p>\n<h3>Bestiality</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:19\">EXO 22:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev18:23\">LEV 18:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:15-Lev20:16\">LEV 20:15–20:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut27:21\">DEU 27:21</a></p>\n<h3>Incest</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev18:6-Lev18:18\">LEV 18:6–18:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:17\">LEV 20:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:19\">LEV 20:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:30\">DEU 22:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut27:20\">DEU 27:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut27:22-Deut27:23\">DEU 27:22–27:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:11\">EZK 22:11</a></p>\n<h3>Intercourse during menstruation</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev18:19\">LEV 18:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:18\">LEV 20:18</a></p>\n<h2>Sexual sin under the new covenant</h2>\n<h3>The OT laws are confirmed and strengthened</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:27-Matt5:28\">MAT 5:27–5:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:31-Matt5:32\">MAT 5:31–5:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:24-Rom1:27\">ROM 1:24–1:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:15-1Cor6:16\">1CO 6:15–6:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:9\">1CO 7:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:4\">HEB 13:4</a></p>\n<h3>The need for holiness in the lives of believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:3-1Thess4:7\">1TH 4:3–4:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:29\">ACT 15:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:3\">EPH 5:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:16\">HEB 12:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:15-1Pet1:16\">1PE 1:15–1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:44\">LEV 11:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:1-1Pet4:3\">1PE 4:1–4:3</a></p>\n<h3>The church must be kept pure</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:14-Rev2:16\">REV 2:14–2:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:1-1Cor5:5\">1CO 5:1–5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:9-1Cor5:11\">1CO 5:9–5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:20\">REV 2:20</a></p>\n<h2>God's judgment on sexual sin</h2>\n<h3>In this life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:21-Rev2:23\">REV 2:21–2:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:24\">GEN 19:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num25:1-Num25:9\">NUM 25:1–25:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:11-2Sam12:12\">2SA 12:11–12:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:26-Prov7:27\">PRO 7:26–7:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:8\">1CO 10:8</a></p>\n<h3>In the world to come</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:8\">REV 21:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:5-Eph5:6\">EPH 5:5–5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:6\">2PE 2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:7\">JUD 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:14-Rev22:15\">REV 22:14–22:15</a></p>\n<h2>God's power over sexual sin</h2>\n<h3>It can be forgiven</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:10-John8:11\">JHN 8:10–8:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:13\">2SA 12:13</a>; PSA 51:0; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:31-Matt21:32\">MAT 21:31–21:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:36-Luke7:38\">LUK 7:36–7:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:47-Luke7:50\">LUK 7:47–7:50</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:21\">REV 2:21</a></p>\n<h3>Hearts can be changed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:9-1Cor6:11\">1CO 6:9–6:11</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Resisting sexual sin</h2>\n<h3>By remembering God's word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:9\">PSA 119:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:23-Prov6:24\">PRO 6:23–6:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:5\">PRO 7:5</a></p>\n<h3>By resisting temptation</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:6-Gen39:12\">GEN 39:6–39:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:24-Prov7:25\">PRO 7:24–7:25</a></p>\n<h3>By mortifying lust</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:1\">JOB 31:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:29-Matt5:30\">MAT 5:29–5:30</a></p>\n<h3>By living in the Spirit</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:16\">GAL 5:16</a></p>\n<h3>By living for holiness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:19\">ROM 6:19</a></p>\n<h3>By enjoying sex within proper limits</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov5:18-Prov5:20\">PRO 5:18–5:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:2\">1CO 7:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:9\">1CO 7:9</a></p>",
